data.description: Welcome home to Fayetteville. This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch home is located on the corner lot in a beautiful quiet neighborhood. The living room has new wood flooring that continues into the dining area down the hallway and continues into the kitchen. All bedrooms have carpeting. The living room area is large enough for the entire family for game night or just lounging and relaxing. There is a large fireplace that is ready for you to use on cold cozy nights. The kitchen was being renovated so you will be provided the new cabinets to have installed yourself. There are all new appliances, new microwave over the stove, new AC, new furnace, and a new water heater. The master bedroom is situated on the other side of the house alone.  It has a vaulted ceiling, a walk-in closet, a private bath with a nice sized garden tub and a separate shower.  This home has enough yard from the front to the back for all of your family enjoyment.
